<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16783] Race condition deleting clusterstate.json can prevent Solr from starting</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16783</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ZkController attempts to delete the deprecated &lt;tt&gt;clusterstate.json&lt;/tt&gt; file from ZooKeeper if empty on startup. If multiple instances attempt to delete it at the same time one of them will succeed and the others will fail with `NoNodeException`, which bubbles up and causes the instance to fail startup, requiring another restart&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
